#---------------------------------
#Folder structure definition file.
#---------------------------------

#Syntax:

#	Both slash and backslash accepted as path separator
#	Entries end with / considered as folders
#	Entries end with no / considered as files
#	Must not exist operator: ! in the beginning of the line
#	Comment: Lines starting with # considered as comments.

#	All path must be relative to the repo root.
#	Note: use src/ instead of ./src/. Relative paths referring _outside_ to the repo root are not accepted

#Folders must exist: 
src/
docs/
tools/
output/

#Folders must not exist: 
!**/bin/

#Files must exist: 
.gitignore
LICENSE
readme.md